      "text": "(intriguing music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 5970.0,
      "end_time": 8690.0,
      "text": "If one would actually see the map of corruption,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 8690.0,
      "end_time": 10770.0,
      "text": "one would see some countries in which corruption"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 10770.0,
      "end_time": 12780.0,
      "text": "is very prevalent, and some countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 12780.0,
      "end_time": 15260.0,
      "text": "in which it's not so prevalent; it's actually very rare."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17180.0,
      "text": "But this is political corruption."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 17180.0,
      "end_time": 20180.0,
      "text": "This is how, on the large-scale, different states"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 20180.0,
      "end_time": 23600.0,
      "text": "have a predisposition to respect the norms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 23600.0,
      "end_time": 25840.0,
      "text": "to respect the rules, or to not respect them."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 25840.0,
      "end_time": 28910.0,
      "text": "The question is is this global,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 28910.0,
      "end_time": 32590.0,
      "text": "political, societal corruption related"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 32590.000000000004,
