      "text": "will undergo some minor forms of cheating"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 37720.0,
      "end_time": 39949.0,
      "text": "in very simple, day-to-day things."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 39950.0,
      "end_time": 43680.0,
      "text": "So when you live in a society in which, at the large scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 43680.0,
      "end_time": 47440.0,
      "text": "the political values are those of not respecting the norms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 47440.0,
      "end_time": 50650.0,
      "text": "then there is a growing number of low-scale corruption"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 50650.0,
      "end_time": 53100.0,
      "text": "within all the people that live within this country."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 53100.0,
      "end_time": 57300.0,
      "text": "Specifically now, in the world but particularly in the U.S.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 57300.0,
      "end_time": 59449.0,
      "text": "we are seeing a spike of mistrust."
